Organize the files folder for 360 Magicians

360magicians/
│
├── core/                           # Core AI agent logic
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── magician_core.py            # Orchestrates all agents
│   ├── idea_validator.py           # Validates ideas -> validation.json
│   └── project_builder.py          # Builds projects -> builder.json + visual pre-templates
│
├── services/                       # External service integrations
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── pinksync_integration.py     # Real-time accessibility & alerts
│   ├── rag_memory.py               # Interface to RAG AI Studio memory
│   └── elastic_ingest.py           # Push knowledge to Elasticsearch / Vertex AI
│
├── api/                            # FastAPI / Flask endpoints
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── magician_router.py          # /validate-idea, /build-project
│   └── auth.py                     # DeafAuth secured endpoints
│
├── data/                           # Persistent & temp storage
│   ├── idea_submissions.json       # Raw user submissions
│   ├── validation_results.json     # Output from idea_validator
│   └── builder_outputs.json        # Output from project_builder
│
├── utils/                          # Helper functions
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── logger.py                   # Structured logging
│   ├── state_manager.py            # Track agent workflow & steps
│   └── task_queue.py               # Background tasks (Celery/Dramatiq)
│
├── pinkflow_cli/                    # CLI automation layer
│   ├── main.py                      # CLI entry point
│   ├── commands/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── index.py                 # Dry-run indexing command
│   │   └── ingest.py                # Ingest to Elasticsearch / Vertex AI
│   └── utils/                        # CLI helper functions
│
├── pinksync/                        # Accessibility & ASL support
│   ├── mesh.py                      # Real-time alert system
│   └── glosser.py                   # Human-assisted ASL glossing
│
├── community_curation/              # Community validation & moderation
│   ├── app.py                       # FastAPI/Flask interface
│   ├── routes/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   └── curation.py              # Endpoint for suggestions/reviews
│   ├── services/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   └── ai_curator.py            # AI-assisted scoring & ranking
│   └── data/                         # Decision history & temp DB
│
├── config/                          # Global configs & secrets
│   ├── settings.yaml
│   └── iam_permissions.json
│
├── deployments/                     # Docker / Cloud Run / CI-CD
│   ├── Dockerfile
│   ├── docker-compose.yaml
│   └── cloud_run/
│
├── tests/                           # Unit & integration tests
│   ├── test_idea_validator.py
│   ├── test_project_builder.py
│   ├── test_api.py
│   └── test_pinkflow_cli.py
│
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
